stroy-browsing-data-collected-from-chromes-incognito-mode-172121598.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tekken-director-apparently-keeps-getting-requests-to-add-a-waffle-house-stage-211913943.html"><ins>《铁拳》导演显然不断收到添加华夫饼屋舞台的请求</ins></a></h2><h3>他们可以称之为“华夫饼粗糙屋”。</h3><p>对于外行来说，Waffle House 是一家以华夫饼为中心的 24/7 美国食客连锁店，以随机爆发暴力而闻名。这显然是众所周知的，以至于《铁拳》玩家一直在<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tekken-director-apparently-keeps-getting-requests-to-add-a-waffle-house-stage-211913943.html"><ins>请求游戏总监添加华夫饼屋关卡</ins></a>。遗憾的是，这种情况可能不会发生，因为华夫饼屋被指控向工人支付过低工资，并且鉴于上述情况，使他们暴露在不安全的工作环境中。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tekken-director-apparently-keeps-getting-requests-to-add-a-waffle-house-stage-211913943.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-does-your-car-need-a-rear-windshield-111523159.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-does-your-car-need-a-rear-windshield-111523159.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9a55fa19-5695-45b5-bce7-3927c00807c8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Daniel Cooper]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 02 Apr 2024 11:15:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1712049995</ingested><modified> 2024-04-02T09:26:46+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="840" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2F